<figureCitation box="[378,528,1283,1312]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="23.[189,228,1207,1231]" captionTargetBox="[189,1399,433,1178]" captionTargetId="figure-325@23.[189,1399,433,1178]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="Fig. 9. Aenictus villiersi, syntype (CASENT0915327). A, head, dorsal view. B, habitus, lateral view. C, mesosoma, petiole and postpetiole, lateral view. D, mesosoma, petiole and postpetiole, dorsal view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5898841" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5898841/files/figure.png" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Fig. 9 A–D</figureCitation>
